sequenceDiagram
    participant Classifier
    participant Permissions as permissions.ts
    participant DenialTracking as denialTracking.ts
    participant Storage as AppState/localDenialTracking

    Classifier->>Permissions: 分类器拒绝（deny）
    Permissions->>DenialTracking: recordDenial(state)
    DenialTracking-->>Permissions: newState（+1/+1）
    Permissions->>Storage: persistDenialState(newState)
    Permissions->>DenialTracking: shouldFallbackToPrompting(newState)?
    DenialTracking-->>Permissions: false（未达阈值）
    Permissions-->>Caller: deny decision

    Note over Permissions: 再次拒绝...

    Classifier->>Permissions: 分类器拒绝（连续第3次）
    Permissions->>DenialTracking: recordDenial(state)
    DenialTracking-->>Permissions: newState（consecutive=3）
    Permissions->>DenialTracking: shouldFallbackToPrompting(newState)?
    DenialTracking-->>Permissions: true（达到阈值3）
    Permissions-->>Caller: ask decision（降级到交互模式）
